OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FIsrael appears to have carried out a
OL,8,Fhighly coordinated attack on the
OL,9,Fmilitant group Hezbollah inside
OL,10,FLebanon, as ITV News' Senior
OL,11,FInternational Correspondent John
OL,12,FIrvine reports
OL,14,FAt least eight people have been killed
OL,15,F- including members of the militant
OL,16,Fgroup Hezbollah - and more than 2,700
OL,17,Finjured after hundreds of pagers
OL,18,Fexploded in Lebanon, officials have
OL,19,Fsaid.
