OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FHezbollah has said it holds Israel
OL,8,F"fully responsible" for Tuesday's
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the group said: "This
OL,12,Fcriminal and treacherous enemy will
OL,13,Fdefinitely receive a fair punishment
OL,14,Ffor this sinful assault, both in ways
OL,15,Fthat are expected and unexpected."
OL,17,FThe Israeli military did not respond
OL,18,Fwhen approached for comment.
