OL,12,FLebanon's health minister, Firas
OL,13,FAbiad, said at least eight people were
OL,14,Fkilled and 2,750 injured - 200 of them
OL,15,Fcritically.
OL,17,FIranian state news reported that its
OL,18,Fambassador to Lebanon was among those
OL,19,Finjured.
