OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FPhotos and videos shared on social
OL,8,Fmedia showed people in Lebanon's
OL,9,Fcapital, Beirut, with wounds to their
OL,10,Fhands and lower bodies.
OL,12,FOne video shared online appears to
OL,13,Fshow an explosion injuring a man as he
OL,14,Fshopped at a supermarket.
OL,16,FAn apparent explosion can be seen
OL,17,Fcoming from the man's right pocket,
OL,18,Fripping apart a bag he was carrying
OL,19,Fand sending him to the floor injured.
