OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FNearby shoppers can also be seen
OL,8,Frunning for cover after the explosion.
OL,10,FHezbollah leader Hassan Nasrallah
OL,11,Fpreviously warned the group's members
OL,12,Fnot to carry pagers - communications
OL,13,Fdevices which receive and display
OL,14,Fvoice messages.
OL,16,FHe said they could be used by Israel
OL,17,Fto track their movements and carry out
OL,18,Ftargeted strikes.
