OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FLebanon's Health Ministry alerted all
OL,8,Fhospitals to take in emergency
OL,9,Fpatients, and for people who own
OL,10,Fpagers to get away from them. It also
OL,11,Fasked health workers to avoid using
OL,12,Fwireless devices.
OL,14,FA separate Hezbollah official said
OL,15,Fthat new pagers given to Hezbollah
OL,16,Fmembers contained lithium batteries,
OL,17,Fwhich, when overheated, can smoke,
OL,18,Fmelt and, on occasion, catch fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
