OL,3,CAt least eight dead and thousands
OL,4,Cinjured from exploding pagers in
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FRechargeable lithium batteries -
OL,8,Fwhich, when set alight, can burn up to
OL,9,F590C - are used in a range of
OL,10,Fproducts, including mobile phones,
OL,11,Flaptops and electric cars.
OL,13,FThe incident comes at a time of
OL,14,Fheightened tensions between Lebanon
OL,15,Fand Israel.
OL,17,FHezbollah and Israeli forces have been
OL,18,Fclashing near-daily for more than 11
OL,19,Fmonths against the backdrop of war
OL,20,Fbetween Israel and proscribed terror
OL,21,Fgroup Hamas in Gaza.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
